        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for letter of 10 September [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">13326</hi>]</p>  
<p>and for copy of <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi>.</p>  
<p>Reports on <hi rend="italic">Lagerstroemia</hi> experiments.</p> 
            <p>Has been making observations on what happens to plants following heavy rain. Sends CD three specimens to show how dirt attaches to the undersides of leaves.</p>
        </abstract>
